            , and sister of the last witness. I did not send the prisoner on the 28th of August, for a carpet or bed furniture, nor for any article on that day, or the day before. I heard of the loss on the 28th of August.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I met with an old shop mate, and we had some porter, we went on towards Pimlico, and had some more liquor, and fell asleep, and do not know what became of me.</p>
